minikube start - -vm-driver=hyperkit (create and start a cluster along with mentioned hypervisor)

kubectl get nodes (list nodes)

minikube status (current status)

kubectl get pod (get pods)

kubectl get services (get services)

kubectl create (create)

kubectl get deployment (list deployments)

kubectl logs *pod name* (to get logs for a specific pod)

kubectl describe pod pod name (to get description for a specific pod)

kubectl exec -it pod name - - bin/bash (gets the terminal of the pod)

kubectl create deployment *pod name* (create a pod)

kubectl edit deployment *pod name* (to get the config file with default values)

kubectl delete deployment *name of the pod* (delete a pod)
